  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-commodity\">supremely powerful</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Geology Cannon</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Increases both <span class=\"name name-stellar\">explosion damage</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">crater radius</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">地质大炮</span>的<span class=\"name name-commodity\">至强</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块很灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>同时提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">爆炸伤害</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">爆炸范围</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">地质大炮</span>的<span class=\"name name-commodity\">至强</span>提升。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始安装升级。<br><br>同时提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">迸裂伤害</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">迸裂范围</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-commodity\">地質砲</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">最強大</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>強化的項目包括：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">爆炸傷害值</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">爆炸坑半徑</span>。"
  },
